###
Commissioner General Rules
N° 004/2009 of 01/04/2009 modifying and completing Commissioner General Rules n°002/2007 of 15/06/2007 implementing the Law n° 25/2005 of 04/12/2005 on tax procedures
cy’Imisoro   The Commissioner General of the Rwanda   Revenue Authority,   Given Law nº 25/2005 of 04/12/2005 on Tax   procedures especially in its Article 47;   Having reviewed Commissioner General rules n°   002/2007 of 15/06/2007 implementing the Law n°   25/2005 of 04/12/2005 on Tax Procedures,   especially in its Article 23;   Issues the following rules :